"{\n  \"Destination Name\": \"Santorini, Greece\",\n  \"Recommended Duration\": \"5 days\",\n  \"Itinerary\": {\n    \"1 day\": {\n      \"Morning\": \"Start your day with a leisurely walk through the picturesque village of Oia, famous for its stunning white-washed buildings and blue-domed churches. Enjoy the breathtaking views of the caldera.\",\n      \"Lunch\": \"Dine at Ammoudi Fish Tavern, located near the water, offering fresh seafood and traditional Greek dishes with a view of the harbor.\",\n      \"Afternoon\": \"Spend a relaxing afternoon at Perissa Beach, where you can unwind on the unique black sand and take a dip in the crystal-clear waters of the Aegean Sea.\",\n      \"Evening\": \"Experience the magical Santorini sunset from a cliffside restaurant like Santo Winery, where you can savor local wines and enjoy a delicious dinner with an unforgettable panoramic view.\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"Activities\": [\n    \"Exploring charming villages like Oia and Fira\",\n    \"Relaxing on beautiful beaches such as Perissa and Kamari\",\n    \"Enjoying sunset views over the caldera\",\n    \"Sampling local wines and Greek cuisine\"\n  ]\n}"
